2–27</i> (1993)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i>Essay Collection: Literature, Philosophy and Short Stories</i> (2000)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i>Essay Collection: Faith, Christianity and the Church</i> (2000)</span></div>
